#: ../../source/index.rst:9
msgid "``janim-url-assets`` 是一个用于直接从 URL 加载线上素材的 JAnim 插件。"
msgstr ""
"``janim-url-assets`` is a JAnim plugin for loading remote assets directly"
" from URLs."

#: ../../source/index.rst:11
msgid "主要提供了如下的物件："
msgstr "The main provided items are:"

#: ../../source/index.rst:13
msgid ":class:`~.UrlSVGItem` : 从 URL 加载 SVG，并按普通 ``SVGItem`` 使用"
msgstr ":class:`~.UrlSVGItem`: load an SVG from a URL and use it as a normal ``SVGItem``"

#: ../../source/index.rst:15
msgid ":class:`~.UrlImageItem` : 从 URL 加载图片，并按普通 ``ImageItem`` 使用"
msgstr ":class:`~.UrlImageItem`: load an image from a URL and use it as a normal ``ImageItem``"

